- The query groups the data by the rescue ship and other lifeboat details to ensure accurate survival rate calculations.

sql:
SELECT COUNT(crew_id) AS crew_count
  FROM lifeboat_assignments
  WHERE lifeboat_id = 0 AND crew_id IS NOT NULL;

